onLineSrc.orName: Green County Land Records and Mapping Applications
onLineSrc.orDesc: Access to Green County GIS data

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents roads for Green County, Wisconsin in 2019. [To be used by Green County Sheriff's Dispatcher's through their third party E911 dispatching and reporting system created by Spillman Technologies. Data created in conjunction with State E911 update grant. Features were derived from a variety of sources including deeds, descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right of way maps. These source materials were of varying scale and date. This coverage provides a representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels within the County, and is suitable as a reference layer within the County's GIS.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This layer is intended as a base layer for use with other digital data developed by agencies within Green County.]
